SUMMARY:Tampas Downtown River OGreen\, presented by Grow Financial
LOCATION:600 N Ashley Dr. Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Youre in luck! River O Green\, presented by Grow Financial is 
 an annual\, free event to kick off the St. Patricks Day holiday\, as the H
 illsborough River is transformed into a bright shade of green. This day of
  festive fun at Curtis Hixon Waterfront Park will feature live music\, kid
 s activities\, food trucks\, and of course\, beer! Join us on Saturday\, M
 arch 14\, at Curtis Hixon Waterfront Park from 11am  4pm\, as we color the
  Hillsborough River green to channel the luck of the Irish! EVENT LINEUP 1
 0:55am: Irish Color Guard Begins Lead to River 11:00am: Festival River Col
 oring Begins 11:10am-12:10pm: Paddy OFurniture Performance 12:15pm: Finneg
 an Irish Dance Academy Performance 12:45-1:45pm: Irish Buskers Performance
  2pm: Finnegan Irish Dance Academy Performance Parade Begins! 2:30pm: Pet 
 Costume Contest (sponsored by Barrymore Hotel) 3-4pm: Shane Beirne Perform
 ance 4pm: Festival concludes FOOD BEVERAGE VENDORS Coles Snow Cone Factory
  Moms Tacos Mi Cafecito The Brisket Shoppe A Boy Named Sous EVENT SPONSORS
  We would also like to extend a HUGE thank you to this years sponsors: Pre
 senting Sponsor: Grow Financial Other Valued Sponsors: TECO Pirate Water T
 axi The Lost Pearl Craft Tampa City of Tampa Freedom Boat Club Barrymore H
 otel iHeart Radio Kuducom Winters Yonker \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.
 gov/node/185806
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185806
