SUMMARY:Spring Break: Guitar Lab
LOCATION:801 Water Street Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Strum\, make and explore in this hands-on family program inspi
 red by  America at the Crossroads: The Guitar and a Changing Nation . Stop
  by the guitar meet-and-greet to handle picks and strings and try out real
  electric and acoustic guitars. Then make a guitar pick necklace to take h
 ome\, with curated music samples playing throughout the experience. The pr
 ogram runs 11 a.m. to 2 p.m. Monday through Friday\, March 16 to March 20\
 , 2026\, in the Wayne Thomas Gallery and is included with museum admission
 . All ages are welcome\, and it is ideal for families. \n\nPermalink: http
 s://www.tampa.gov/node/185841
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185841
END:VEVENT
