 ess space on Morgan St to build separated bike lanes from Brorein St to Ha
 rrison St on the west side of the road. The roadway will be resurfaced\, a
 nd new signs and pavement markings installed. Parking and necessary travel
  lanes will be maintained. This project will make Morgan St safer and more
  livable while preserving important capacity on the roadway during events 
 at Benchmark International Arena. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/nod
 e/185716
