SUMMARY:2026 Dusk til Dawn Sleepout
LOCATION:6718 N. Armenia Ave Tampa \, FL 33604 United States
DESCRIPTION:This night is more than just an event  its a movement to bring
  hope and stability to families facing homelessness in Hillsborough County
 . By joining us\, you are not just attending an event\\\; you are becoming
  a beacon of change for those who need it the most. Be a part of a night f
 illed with a community united for a common cause. This fully experiential 
 event features peer to peer fundraising\, live music\, hands-on activities
 \, community engagement and a transformational evening hosted by Tampas ow
 n Sarah Rosario as we sleepout in solidarity for homelessness at our campu
 s. Youll know that every moment spent is making a direct impact on familie
 s striving for a brighter future. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/nod
