SUMMARY:Charter Review Commission Meeting
LOCATION:Tampa Old City Hall - Sister Cities Room 315 East Kennedy Bouleva
 rd Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:CHARTER REVIEW ADVISORY COMMISSION MEETING Date: Tuesday\, Apr
 il 14\, 2026 Time: 6:00pm to 9:00pm Location: Old City Hall  Sister Cities
  Room 315 East Kennedy Boulevard Tampa\, Florida 33602 Facilitator Robert 
 Hendrickson will facilitate meetings of the 2025 Charter Review Advisory C
 ommission. The commissions purpose is to review the Tampa Home Rule Charte
 r of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by majori
 ty vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendation
 s to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be placed
  on the ballot for a vote on March 2\, 2027. Meetings are scheduled monthl
 y for the 2 nd and 4 th Tuesday. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node
 /180051
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/180051
END:VEVENT
