SUMMARY:Yoga Classes at Hanna City Center
LOCATION:Hanna City Center in the Hanna Community Room 2555 E. Hanna Avenu
 e Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:REGISTER HERE Employees must register in advance. 10-person mi
 nimum or class will be cancelled and each class is capped at 30 participan
 ts so please register early. Every other Monday from 5:15PM  6:00PM at Han
 na City Center in the Hanna Community Room. The address is: 2555 E. Hanna 
 Avenue in Tampa\, 33610 Please note: These classes are for City of Tampa e
 mployees only and you will be asked to sign a waiver at each session. If y
 ou have any questions about these Yoga or strength training classes\, plea
